<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 11" captionStartId="22.[160,225,1276,1299]" captionTargetBox="[163,1153,142,1244]" captionTargetId="figure-144@22.[163,1153,142,1244]" captionTargetPageId="22" captionText="Figure 11. Aleuromarginatus martini Dubey sp. nov.: (a) adult male; (b) antenna, compound eye; (c) abdominal wax plates; (d) lingula, genitalia." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6000807" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6000807/files/figure.png" pageId="24" pageNumber="2629">Figure 11</figureCitation>
